flowchart LR
    OMS[Shipment booking] --> ROUTE[Carrier router]
    ROUTE --> ADP1[Delhivery adapter]
    ROUTE --> ADP2[Bluedart adapter]
    ROUTE --> ADP3[Ekart adapter]
    ROUTE --> ADPN[... N more adapters]
    ROUTE --> ADPF[Pikshipp Express adapter]

    ADP1 --> CRR[Courier APIs]
    ADP2 --> CRR
    ADP3 --> CRR
    ADPN --> CRR
    ADPF --> CRR

    CRR -- webhooks --> WHK[Webhook receiver]
    CRR -- polled --> POLLER[Polling worker]
    WHK --> NORM[Status normalizer]
    POLLER --> NORM
    NORM --> TRACK[Tracking ctx]
